<br>
Assuming you are pulling to the Ruins (East) side of the lake, and already have your kiting kit (SoTF, Lev, and Sow,Jboots)<br>
<br>
Pull your first two from the Square tower. <br>
Target the farthest of the two.<br>
then swim halfway to the pillard spawn and flux.<br>
hit ESC to clear your target and while swimming to the pillard spawn<br>
mash F8 till you get another Bloodgill on target.<br>
Point yourself straight up, NumLock to start moving, then flux your second gobby<br>
Once you hit the surfact, Hit HOME key to face foward and pull your catch to shore.<br>
Now Kite till dead and collect PHAT XP, and repeat.<br>
<br>
I took some hits getting this down, but steel skin kept me from taking too much damage. The ONLY time I have died from this is when I hit the stupid frigging Windows key on my keyboard and got dropped to desktop. I tried to alt tab back, but got a blank screen. I ended up dead, but got the xp back one kite later. Ahh the wonders of quadding<br>
